==Russian==
[[Category:Russian pronouns]]
===Demonstrative pronoun===
'''сей''', сия, сие, сии (sej, sijá, sijé, sií) ''m/f/n/pl''

# [[this]], this here

====Usage note====
Сей is an archaic form that is no longer used in speech or in prose unless compounded with other words or in certain set phrases:
#:*{{RUchar|[[сегодня|сего́дня]]}} — ''today''
#:*{{RUchar|[[сейчас|сейча́с]]}} — ''immediately''
#:*{{RUchar|сию [[минута|мину́ту]]}} — ''this very minute''
#:*{{RUchar|до сих [[пор]]}} — ''until now''
#:*{{RUchar|[[и#Russian|и]] то и сё}} — ''both this and the other''
#:*{{RUchar|то [[да#Russian|да]] сё}} — ''one thing and another''
#:*{{RUchar|[[ни]] то ни сё}} — ''neither the one nor the other''

